    dxf: Fix null-deref in dwg_dxfb_PROXY_ENTITY
    
    * src/dwg.spec: Guard DXF objids loop with _obj->objids NULL check.
      PROXY_ENTITY can have num_objids > 0 but objids == NULL,
      causing a SEGV at _obj->objids[rcount1].
      Fixes oss-fuzz 530762732 / testcase 6079304832974848
    
    Co-authored-by: omp + DeepSeek V4 Pro <deepseek@deepseek.com>

diff --git a/src/dwg.spec b/src/dwg.spec
